  m_Name: Trunk
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::CodexEntry
  title: Trunk
  description: 'Trunks were large storage containers used for clothing, textiles,
    and personal belongings. They were commonly used for travel or long-term storage
    before modern suitcases became widespread. In large households, trunks also served
    as a way to organize seasonal clothing or transport possessions between estates. '
